", "score": 0, "rich_text": false } ], "skill_area": 1105219, "status": "active", "state": "new", "order": 2, "has_changed": false, "has_versions": false, "duration": 0, "previous_version": null, "identifier": "Q00.002", "code_language": null, "initial_code": null, "correct_code": "not-applicable", "return_type": "str", "function_name": null, "code_params": [], "code_test_cases": [], "sql_return_type": "SELECT", "initial_sql": null, "sql_test_cases": [], "typing_test_type": null, "typing_test_config": null, "typing_test_mode": { "numbers": false, "punctuation": false, "funbox": "none", "sentences": false }, "long_answer_list": false, "max_items": 100, "min_items": 0, "scale": 5, "custom_question_id": 901384, "what_to_look_for_in_the_answer": "", "why_is_this_question_relevant": "", "title": "", "category": [], "language": "en", "default_language": "en", "resources": [], "boilerplates": [], "programming_solutions": [], "test_cases": [], "test_version_number": 1 }, { "id": 901385, "text": "

", "intro_text": null, "type": "multiple-choice", "shuffle": true, "answers": [ { "id": 7985742, "text": "

{ "id": 2730216, "name": "B2C Telesales (Multimedia)", "summary": "This multimedia B2C Telesales test evaluates a candidate’s ability to sell business-to-consumer products over the phone, whether calls are inbound or outbound. This test will help you hire employees who can close deals and maintain customer relationships.", "duration": 780.0, "estimated_duration": null, "type": [ { "id": 6, "name": "Role-specific skills", "visible": true } ], "is_new": false, "content_type_name": "test_authoring.test", "default_language": "en", "description": "Hiring B2C telesales representatives with strong communication and sales skills can be a game changer for every company. In addition to raising awareness about your brand and products and expanding your business reach to more prospects, telesales agents with great abilities can boost your sales and conversion rates while building stronger relationships with potential and existing clients.\n \nThis multimedia B2C Telesales test evaluates candidates’ abilities to set targets and plan sales activities, build trust and rapport with customers, pitch products, and handle rejection, stress, and conflict.\n\nThis screening test will help you identify telesales representatives and remote inside sales agents with the right sales, communication, and interpersonal skills to boost your sales revenue. Candidates who do well on this test will generate new B2C sales opportunities, convert prospects into paying clients, and build deeper connections with customers. This test features a combination of video-based and text-based questions.", "relevant": "B2C inbound and/or outbound telesales representatives, B2C remote sales agents, B2C inside sales professionals, B2C telemarketers, and other sales roles handling inside sales in B2C organizations.", "job_roles": [ 5905, 5906, 3107, 3110 ], "owner": { "id": 418805, "biography": "Hasnaa is a sales trainer who has worked as a sales manager and sales team leader and has sold products and services to hundreds of B2C and B2B clients. After spending 20 years in marketing and sales around the world, she has concluded that there is one universal truth: \"A customer needs to be seen, heard and deeply cared about.\" When not working, she loves contemplating nature, and studying spirituality, human behavior and the psychology of sales, as well as simply enjoying the beauty of life.", "country": null, "image": "https://tgo-public-assets-production.s3.amazonaws.com/production/3f4f190a-8c31-4dce-bbb8-b3efa83b0ecb-9355bbdf-906c-4348-950c-eb501bad42e3.png", "full_name": "Hasnaa B.", "url": null }, "level": "intermediate", "language": "en", "covered_skills": [ { "id": 2799594, "description": "Preview questions", "preview": true }, { "id": 2799595, "description": "Setting targets and planning sales activities", "preview": false }, { "id": 2799596, "description": "Building trust and rapport with customers", "preview": false }, { "id": 2799597, "description": "Pitching products", "preview": false }, { "id": 2799598, "description": "Handling rejection, stress, and conflict", "preview": false } ], "preview_questions": [ { "id": 2097979, "text": "

You work for a fitness center that maintains a database containing exhaustive information about potential leads, including age, gender, address, previous gym membership purchases, and attendance to prior free events. Your daily target is to contact 60 new leads within two hours to introduce a new gym membership. After one hour today, you called only 15 prospects. Most did not pick up the phone. Those you spoke to did not qualify for the offer.

 

What should you do next?

", "intro_text": null, "type": "multiple-choice", "shuffle": true, "answers": [ { "id": 19889077, "text": "

Identify 45 warm leads in the database, such as those who previously purchased a membership or often attend free events.

", "score": 5, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889078, "text": "

Quickly check in with your manager for suggestions on improving your approach.

", "score": 1, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889079, "text": "

Review and adjust the script to determine whether the lead is qualified for the offer, with a target of less than two minutes per lead.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889080, "text": "

Analyze why the leads did not qualify for the offer to better select the next 45 prospects.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false } ], "skill_area": 2799594, "status": "active", "state": "new", "order": 1, "has_changed": false, "has_versions": true, "duration": 0, "previous_version": 521826, "identifier": "Q00.001", "code_language": null, "initial_code": null, "correct_code": "not-applicable", "return_type": "str", "function_name": null, "code_params": [], "code_test_cases": [], "sql_return_type": "SELECT", "initial_sql": null, "sql_test_cases": [], "typing_test_type": null, "typing_test_config": null, "typing_test_mode": { "numbers": false, "punctuation": false, "funbox": "none", "sentences": false }, "long_answer_list": false, "max_items": 100, "min_items": 0, "scale": 5, "custom_question_id": 521826, "what_to_look_for_in_the_answer": "", "why_is_this_question_relevant": "", "title": "", "category": [], "language": "en", "default_language": "en", "resources": [], "boilerplates": [], "programming_solutions": [], "test_cases": [], "test_version_number": 2 }, { "id": 2097980, "text": "

You work for a life coach who proposes high-ticket coaching programs to women on “how to discover and live their life’s purpose,” with an entry price of $7,000 per program. Women interested in joining the program complete an application form and receive a follow-up call to assess whether they qualify. During one of your follow-up calls, a woman explains, “I’m very interested in joining, but I still need to discuss it with my husband.”

 

How should you respond?

", "intro_text": null, "type": "multiple-choice", "shuffle": true, "answers": [ { "id": 19889081, "text": "

Thank her for the time she spent with you and ask her to contact you once she has discussed it with her husband.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889082, "text": "

Ask for a follow-up call with her and her husband to share the program’s benefits directly with him.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889083, "text": "

Ask if there is anything you can do to support her as she talks to her husband, and book another follow-up call with her.

", "score": 5, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889084, "text": "

Highlight more benefits of the program, and book another follow-up call with her.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false } ], "skill_area": 2799594, "status": "active", "state": "new", "order": 2, "has_changed": false, "has_versions": true, "duration": 0, "previous_version": 521827, "identifier": "Q00.002", "code_language": null, "initial_code": null, "correct_code": "not-applicable", "return_type": "str", "function_name": null, "code_params": [], "code_test_cases": [], "sql_return_type": "SELECT", "initial_sql": null, "sql_test_cases": [], "typing_test_type": null, "typing_test_config": null, "typing_test_mode": { "numbers": false, "punctuation": false, "funbox": "none", "sentences": false }, "long_answer_list": false, "max_items": 100, "min_items": 0, "scale": 5, "custom_question_id": 521827, "what_to_look_for_in_the_answer": "", "why_is_this_question_relevant": "", "title": "", "category": [], "language": "en", "default_language": "en", "resources": [], "boilerplates": [], "programming_solutions": [], "test_cases": [], "test_version_number": 2 }, { "id": 2097981, "text": "

You work for a company that provides transport services to individuals for fixed, non-negotiable prices and free additional services to increase customer loyalty. You receive a call from a client needing a last-minute driver and VIP car for a trip to a party on the same day. You give her the quote, and she says, “It’s too expensive. Are you able to reduce the price?”

 

What should you say next to move the sale forward?

", "intro_text": null, "type": "multiple-choice", "shuffle": true, "answers": [ { "id": 19889085, "text": "

Suggest a standard car rather than a VIP one, and state the new price quote.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889086, "text": "

Politely explain that the rate is non-negotiable, but emphasize that the company is highly rated, so the service is worth the rate.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889087, "text": "

Politely explain that the rate is non-negotiable, and offer her a free additional service.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889088, "text": "

Ask more questions about her budget and what is most important for her during this trip.

", "score": 5, "rich_text": false } ], "skill_area": 2799594, "status": "active", "state": "new", "order": 3, "has_changed": false, "has_versions": true, "duration": 0, "previous_version": 521828, "identifier": "Q00.003", "code_language": null, "initial_code": null, "correct_code": "not-applicable", "return_type": "str", "function_name": null, "code_params": [], "code_test_cases": [], "sql_return_type": "SELECT", "initial_sql": null, "sql_test_cases": [], "typing_test_type": null, "typing_test_config": null, "typing_test_mode": { "numbers": false, "punctuation": false, "funbox": "none", "sentences": false }, "long_answer_list": false, "max_items": 100, "min_items": 0, "scale": 5, "custom_question_id": 521828, "what_to_look_for_in_the_answer": "", "why_is_this_question_relevant": "", "title": "", "category": [], "language": "en", "default_language": "en", "resources": [], "boilerplates": [], "programming_solutions": [], "test_cases": [], "test_version_number": 2 }, { "id": 2097982, "text": "

You work for a company selling online educational children’s programs to parents. Today, you are calling an existing database of parents to introduce them to a new children’s program the company has just launched. A man answers your first call. After introducing yourself, the client angrily interrupts you, explains that he is not happy with the current program he uses, and asks for a refund. You are not familiar with this program.

 

How can you best react to this client?

", "intro_text": null, "type": "multiple-choice", "shuffle": true, "answers": [ { "id": 19889089, "text": "

Acknowledge his point of view, and question him further on areas he felt the company did not deliver what he was expecting for his child.

", "score": 5, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889090, "text": "

Assess his level of anger and decide whether to transfer the call to someone familiar with the program for which he wants a refund.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889091, "text": "

Empathize with him about his previous negative experience, take his information to organize his refund, then put your focus on presenting your new offer.

", "score": 0, "rich_text": false }, { "id": 19889092, "text": "

Thank him for his honesty, take his information to organize his refund, and make a note to call back once the refund is processed.
